Spears::

She leaned against the wall and slid down into a sitting possision. 
She shook her head. She tried to think.  She had to access the 
programs that might still be.  She closed her eyes and tried as hard 
as she could. She couldn't find the programs in her memory or any 
other programs. She shook and cried where she was. "It's not there. I 
can't find it. I don't know it." She cried and covered her face with 
her hands.
